REMARKS : Alien species in the Mediterranean Sea, with origin from New Zealand (Pacific Ocean) (
Read 2007
;
Zenetos et al. 2010
). The presence in the Adriatic Sea is uncertain; specimens were found in 1992 by Castelli (unpublished data) in Sacca Barbamarco, near the Po River delta (
Castelli et al. 2008
).

